										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_0 et_section_regular" >
				
				
				
				
					<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_0">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_0  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_0  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p><strong>A new version of the Fields plugin is now available!</strong></p>
<p>This version corrects a recently discovered security problem. The update is recommended!</p>
<ul>
<li>CVE-2024-45600 Authenticated SQL Injection</li>
</ul>
<p>The <a href="https://github.com/pluginsGLPI/fields/blob/1.21.13/CHANGELOG.md">full changelog</a> is available for more details.</p>
<p>You can update the plugin from the marketplace or download the plugin archive on <a href="https://github.com/pluginsGLPI/fields/releases/tag/1.21.13">GitHub</a>.</p></div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
