										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote has-medium-font-size">
<p>Congratulations! We are happy to announce our new Silver GLPI Network partner in France: <strong>ITSR Informatique</strong></p>
</blockquote>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="535" src="https://glpi-project.org/wp-content/uploads/EN-15-1024x535.png" alt="" class="wp-image-431735" srcset="https://glpi-project.org/wp-content/uploads/EN-15-1024x535.png 1024w, https://glpi-project.org/wp-content/uploads/EN-15-980x512.png 980w, https://glpi-project.org/wp-content/uploads/EN-15-480x251.png 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) 1024px, 100vw" /></figure>



